<14>1 2024-01-15T10:00:26.000Z myhost myapp 1234 ID48 [exampleSDID@32473 iut="5" eventSource="Database" eventID="2001"] Database connection established
<11>1 2024-01-15T10:00:27.000Z myhost myapp 1234 ID49 [exampleSDID@32473 iut="9" eventSource="Security" eventID="3001"] Failed login attempt: user=root from=10.0.0.99
